<title>LATVIA: AKTA NET LOSS 180,488 LATS.</title>
<headline>AKTA NET LOSS 180,488 LATS.</headline>
<dateline>RIGA 1997-08-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>First half 1997</p>
<p>					(million lats unless stated)</p>
<p> Net loss					    180,488 lats</p>
